# snap
    :Snap is a package management system developed by Canonical.
____________________________________

> snap [COMMAND]

    [COMMAND]
        list
            :display a list of snap packages.

        info
            :information of a package.
            
        refresh [PACKAGE]
            :update a package

        install
            :install a package

        remove
            :remove a package

        
## EXAMPLES
    > sudo snap refresh firefox